if you are real fan of this qawali then definitely you will not like this version. Atif doesn't has voice quality, variation and power to properly render this qawali. Thats why Rohail never touched it. Bilal is good musician and I like his music very much but coke studio is not his cup of tea. Better option was if it would be given to some real qawal. Offcourse little research was required of this task tpo get proper voice but who take the pain. its simple to call atif, ali etc and ask them to sing whatever you want them to sing.
But if you have heard this qawali once of twice in your lifde then you will like this version

It's always heart warming to hear tribute to God by other muslims from another part of the world. This is how Pakistan should be viewed, as a Land of pure talent, freshness, spirituality and Love.

God bless y'all, including listeners from other religions (hindus, sikhs, christians,etc) and lots of love from Morocco!  ❤ ❤
